    • Enum Constant Detail

      • NEW

        public static final OrderState NEW
        Order is new, never submitted to the broker.

      • PENDING_SUBMIT

        public static final OrderState PENDING_SUBMIT
        Has been sent to the broker.

      • PROCESSING

        public static final OrderState PROCESSING
        order has been submitted by the broker and is now processed Partial fills do not change the order's state from here to filled.

      • FILLED

        public static final OrderState FILLED
        Order is filled, only if is complete. Partial filling is not considered a filled order. This is the terminal state of an order, no further changes to the Order state or values are allowed. This is a terminal state.

      • REJECTED

        public static final OrderState REJECTED
        Order has been rejected by the broker. No executions were done. This is a terminal state on an Order.

      • CANCELED

        public static final OrderState CANCELED
        Broker confirmed that Order was successfully canceled (at user's request). Order may still be partially filled.

      • PENDING_CANCEL

        public static final OrderState PENDING_CANCEL
        User requested to cancel this Order. Broker received the request, but is still evaluating the request.

      • EXPIRED

        public static final OrderState EXPIRED
        Order has expired.
